      "full_text" : "@jordanglee With pleasure @jordanglee!\n\nBasically, The SAT is too easy at the top.\n\nHigh scores are common enough that they don't differentiate. \n\nSo admissions looks elsewhere—essays, extracurriculars, \"leadership.\" All of which favor kids with resources and coaching.",
