      "created_at" : "Fri May 05 15:17:43 +0000 2023",
      "favorited" : false,
      "full_text" : "4) We know #Introspection is hard. Doing it by yourself is even harder. Pressure to “just #apply” means people don't think about what they want or why they're good for a role. It also means they submit the same rez and CL for most roles. Sadly, that just doesn't cut it.",
