      "created_at" : "Fri May 05 15:17:43 +0000 2023",
      "favorited" : false,
      "full_text" : "3) Meanwhile, #jobboards suck to be on. Who needs another #disruptive unicorn that's ultimately still filtering people by degree and school? To do better, you need to build from the ground up",
      "lang" : "en",
      "in_reply_to_screen_name" : "thevibethinker",
