      "favorited" : false,
      "full_text" : "2) Also, in the #ChatGPT era, it's easier than ever to buff (or even fake) your #resume/#coverletter, but what's the point if you can't *actually* talk about what sets you apart in an interview? Feels like progress in the short term, pretty much self-defeating in the long run",
